name: Orman_Tagge
content:
Orman Tagge was a human male who served as Head of Manufacturing at the Tagge Corporation during the Galactic Civil War. A scion of the House of Tagge, he was an older brother of Domina Tagge, who helmed the company. Orman wore goggles or other over-eye instruments.
Orman Tagge first canonically appeared in an imagination spot in the fifth issue of the 2020 comic series Star Wars: Doctor Aphra . He first appeared in-person and was first identified in the 2021 comic War of the Bounty Hunters â€“ Boushh 1. Orman Tagge originated in the Star Wars Legends continuity, where he first appeared in the twenty-fifth issue of the original 1977 Marvel Comics Star Wars comic.
